Did'nt He tell you, \uc0\u8232 \'93Fear not, little flock, for it is your Father's good pleasure to give you the Kingdom\'94.\
\
2 \'96 Glory.\
This brings me to the second point, Glory.\
Glory and Moral perfection IS THE KINGDOM!\
